thread.title_full: DynaFile reviewed by Kerry Crutchley at Central One Federal CU

author: Kerry Crutchley at Central One Federal CU
title: Kerry Crutchley at Central One Federal CU
text: The Dynafile training was well put together. Lyndsay was always available to answer my questions. One thing that is important to me is whether a company is willing to work with my requests. I am okay with a "no" answer but only after an effort is made to try to meet my request. Lyndsay always worked with her team to try and meet my company's needs and she always found a solution! Thank you!
